{"tid":964754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"O記拘7男女　檢19支槍逾700發子彈","createTime":"2019-01-01T14:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T13:46:04.000Z","uid":56810,"like":14,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"481dcad9953962fcf28921736bfc6d1c9d01d6bf","tid":964754,"uid":56810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190101/photo/bkn-20190101220538598-0101_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190101221718\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190101%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190101220538598-0101_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190101221718&h=8de6fb20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方早前接獲線報，指有人無牌管有一批槍械及組件。O記經深入調查後，昨日（31日）及今日（1日），突擊搜查全港共13個單位及地點，拘捕5名本地男子及2名本地女子，年齡介乎17至53歲，涉嫌「無牌管有槍械及彈藥」及／或「意圖危害生命而管有槍械或彈藥」。<br />\n<br />\n行動中，警方共檢取1支手槍、11支仿製長槍、7支仿製手槍、超過700發槍械子彈及2件槍械組件。警方亦檢取了電腦和其他相關物品以追查槍械的來源及用途。警方行動仍在進行中。"},{"pid":"6fcbb7c076f8ce2f02abe5ac829bdebc180de2cb","tid":964754,"uid":107364,"like":6,"dislike":83,"score":-77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fede7b3943734869b936f2e1e6b27ce5ea14d02a","tid":964754,"uid":30169,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"Wargame ？"},{"pid":"468ae64c3b2f684e4a019af79a05ebe75504970c","tid":964754,"uid":15503,"like":171,"dislike":1,"score":170,"quote":{"pid":"6fcbb7c076f8ce2f02abe5ac829bdebc180de2cb","tid":964754,"uid":107364,"like":6,"dislike":83,"score":-77,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:31:38.000Z","msg":"行動中，警方共檢取<span style=\"color: red;\">1支手槍、11支仿製長槍、7支仿製手槍</span>、超過700發槍械子彈及2件槍械組件。<br />\n<br />\n字面意思係有一支真槍喎"},{"pid":"e51433bb52e58e062e4ca6218b37dbf47c10b53b","tid":964754,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":130,"score":-129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:32:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58797fbcea853cb0f6f6a2fbd83e8d62475ba7e4","tid":964754,"uid